Credit Agricole Cheuvreux Names Goodman CEO Effective Sept. 1

-- B y   V i d y a   R o o t
-- 
2011-09-19T15:13:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/credit-agricole-cheuvreux-names-goodman-ceo-effective-sept-1.html
Credit Agricole Cheuvreux named
Jeremy Goodman its chief executive offiver effective Sept. 1.
Goodman replaces Jean-Claude Bassein, who has been appinted
global chief operating officer in  Hong Kong , charged with
integrating CA Cheuvreux and CLSA, the bank said in an e-mailed
statement.  Jonathan Slone, chairman and CEO of CLSA, has been named
chairman of CA Cheuvreux.  The changes stem from the equity brokerage partnership
between Credit Agricole CIB and CITIC Securities announced in
June, the bank said,  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vidya Root at 
 vroot@bloomberg.net  